column1: Expression of BX-C genes across color form/metasomal segment M2 and M3 /pupal stages in B.melanopygus worker

If multiple plates are runned, dilution series were ran for each qPCR plate, a specific curve for each genes was obtained for each plate.  EQUATIOINS on one plate only apply to qPCR reactions carried out on the same plate
Calculation of AGM from standard curves
Expression of relative expression on graph=Log2AGM (target gene)/AGM (vATPase)

#  speciemen names is given as colony number-pupal stage-sex-bee number. For example, 38-S9-male-2 means the second stage 9 male pupae collected from colony number 38. Colony information can be found at the last tab (speciemen information) of this document
* hc=hour callow. It stands for hours after a callow emerges from cocoon
